WEBVTT

00:05.588 --> 00:08.841
Charlie Brown. Oh, Charlie Brown.

00:10.885 --> 00:12.553
I can't believe it.

00:12.720 --> 00:16.097
She must think
I'm the most stupid person alive.

00:20.978 --> 00:24.690
Come on, Charlie Brown.
I'll hold the ball and you kick it.

00:27.068 --> 00:28.778
Hold it? Ha!

00:29.028 --> 00:33.074
You'll pull it away and I'll land
flat on my back and kill myself.

00:33.950 --> 00:36.911
But Charlie Brown, it's Thanksgiving.

00:37.078 --> 00:39.622
What's that got to do with anything?

00:41.165 --> 00:43.292
Why, one of the greatest traditions
we have

00:43.501 --> 00:45.211
is the Thanksgiving Day football game.

00:45.378 --> 00:50.091
And the biggest, most important tradition
of all is the kicking off of the football.

00:51.175 --> 00:52.802
Is that right?

00:53.427 --> 00:57.431
Absolutely. Come on, Charlie Brown.
It's a big honor for you.

01:01.477 --> 01:04.021
Well, if it's that important,

01:04.188 --> 01:07.358
a person should never turn down
a big honor.

01:08.568 --> 01:10.736
Maybe I should do it.

01:14.615 --> 01:19.495
Besides, she wouldn't try to trick me
on a traditional holiday.

01:21.080 --> 01:24.667
This time I'm gonna kick that football
clear to the moon.

